  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">as regards the principal pleasure of the act itself of procreation, there is " chastity ," and as to the pleasures incidental to the act, resulting, for instance, from kissing , touching, or fondling, we have "purity." The potential parts of a principal virtue are ca</data>
