  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">he word " chastity " is employed in two ways. First, properly; and thus it is a special virtue having a special matter , namely the concupiscences relating to venereal pleasures. Secondly, the word " chastity " is employed metaphorically: for just as a mingling of bodies co</data>
