  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">As Isidore says (Etym. x), "a lustful man is one who is debauched with pleasures." Now venereal pleasures above all debauch a man's mind. Therefore lust is especially concerned with such like pleasures.</data>
