  <data key="d16">explicit_textual</data>
  <data key="d17">erefore he severed clemency also from modesty, and held modesty to be about the remaining ordinary matters that require moderation. These seemingly are of four kinds. one is the movement of the mind towards some excellence, and this is moderated by " humility ." The second is the desir</data>
